PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of KEVIN G. LYNCH, Deputy Minister of Industry, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada for a term of three years, in the place of Harry Swain; and appointment of ALAN B. NYMARK, Assistant Deputy Minister, Industry and Science Policy, Department of Industry, to act as director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada for Kevin G. Lynch, in the place of Charles Stedman.
